@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rkewyn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.cos(wp.abs(v0 + 0.13)))
    v0 = (v0 * (v2 / wp.abs(v2 + 0.37)))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.exp(wp.exp(v2 + 0.09)))
    v1 = v0
    tmp = (wp.sin(v1) / wp.sin((v2 + 0.49 - tmp + 0.44)))
    data[tid] = v0
